  "detailed_description": "<strong>Welcome to GhoulScrapers.</strong><br><br>Ghoulscrapers is a precision platformer where you play as Eggroll, the new employee at Ghoulscrapers.<br>You owe the government one gazillion dollars and it's your job to pay the debt before it's too late!<br><br>Ghoulscrapers have also given you a shotgun but that's neither here nor there.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast paced gameplay!<br></li><li> Precision platforming!<br></li><li> Fun colorful cast!<br></li><li> Plenty of collectables!<br></li><li> A fish! (?)</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843550/extras/5c21505cb01429299b9ef991bce917d5.avif?t=1736294827\" width=520 height=459 /></span>",
